#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/units/Dark_Queen.cfg:25
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/units/Dark_Queen.cfg:110
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/units/Youth.cfg:25
